{"data":[{"id":561510667,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"20a871f0dc314516fede0187d7505fd3","url_token":"shawn-76-29","name":"shawn","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a4517bdbb89e85d85a57b2c23bec678d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a4517bdbb89e85d85a57b2c23bec678d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/20a871f0dc314516fede0187d7505fd3","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":649,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561510667","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545974043,"updated_time":1545974043,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e绝对不可能有高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e凡是有高中生说自己能证明哥德巴赫猜想，那一定是在胡说八道。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别误会， 我不否认数学天才的存在。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但问题的关键是， 如果是数学天才，一定会很小的时候展示出过人的数学天赋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e任何人，任何事物都是这样的，总有个循序渐进的过程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果一个短跑天才，十几岁就能破世界纪录，那也一定先是幼儿园的时候就跑的比别的小朋友快，然后体校，然后省冠军，全国冠军，世界冠军。怎么可能睡着睡着突然有一题就去拿金牌了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同样的道理， 即使是一个前所未有的数学天才，也一定要一步一步的学习基础数学知识，高等数学，数论，必须一步一步来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，正常来说一个数学天才的轨迹应该是，从小展现过人的数学天赋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后小学时完成初中，高中的课程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在初高中阶段（15~16岁），破格被大学录取。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在同龄孩子上高中的阶段， 完成高等数学教育。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在同龄孩子上大学的阶段， 开始完成研究生学业。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也就是说， 不管还是有史以来最厉害的数学天才，还是普通 人，想要证明哥德巴赫猜想，前期需要学习的数学知识，都必须一步一步学完了，一个都不能少。  唯一的区别是，天才可能用你一半的时间学完所有课程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e但是，绝对不可能，天才不学无数，仅仅具备初等数学的知识，就莫名其妙的证明了哥德巴赫猜想！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果有人告诉你，他什么都不懂，什么数学都没学过，仅仅掌握初等数学知识。睡着睡着，然后有一天突然证明了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e那他不是骗子就是神经病。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e古今中外这种骗子神棍还少吗？  \u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e长点心吧，别再相信这些东西了。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"\u003cb\u003e绝对不可能有高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/b\u003e凡是有高中生说自己能证明哥德巴赫猜想，那一定是在胡说八道。别误会， 我不否认数学天才的存在。但问题的关键是， 如果是数学天才，一定会很小的时候展示出过人的数学天赋。任何人，任何事物都是这样的，总有个循序渐…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026off